character.name: Isometric pixel art character of a male office worker in his mid 30s, once a talented and respected employee but now broken and bitter after being betrayed by a colleague. He wears a slightly wrinkled grey suit with a loosened tie and a faintly unshaven face. His dark brown hair is messy, and his expression shows sadness mixed with restrained anger and exhaustion. Eyes slightly downcast, lips pressed tight, eyebrows furrowed. Standing with slouched posture, holding an old briefcase loosely in one hand. The color tone is muted and cool to emphasize his despair and frustration. Transparent background, clean edges, consistent with 2D isometric RPG game style.
